WEBVTT

00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:03.124
Wow, wow, people.

00:00:03.124 --> 00:00:07.795
You know, actually, I love people
because my work is about people.

00:00:08.379 --> 00:00:10.882
It's actually about bringing
people together.

00:00:11.382 --> 00:00:12.550
I'm an artist.

00:00:12.550 --> 00:00:14.177
I mean, until I found a real job,

00:00:14.218 --> 00:00:16.596
but now it looks
like it's getting pretty serious.

00:00:16.637 --> 00:00:18.014
(Laughter)

00:00:18.014 --> 00:00:20.141
But, you know, I also love walls.

00:00:20.141 --> 00:00:23.519
And I know that walls
are supposed to divide us,

00:00:23.561 --> 00:00:26.064
but I think I've found a way

00:00:26.105 --> 00:00:28.191
to use walls to bring us together.

00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:30.651
And I've tried this in different places.